# IslamWiki Version History

## Version 0.0.18 (2025-07-30)
- **Added**: Hybrid Configuration System with MediaWiki-inspired structure
- **Added**: LocalSettings.php with 108 comprehensive configuration settings
- **Added**: IslamSettings.php as optional Islamic override file
- **Added**: ConfigurationManager for unified configuration management
- **Added**: ConfigurationServiceProvider for service container integration
- **Added**: 8 global helper functions for easy configuration access
- **Added**: Configuration validation with error/warning reporting
- **Added**: Comprehensive test suite with 15 test categories
- **Added**: Islamic-focused configuration sections
- **Added**: Performance-optimized configuration loading and caching
- **Added**: Environment integration with .env file support
- **Added**: MediaWiki-inspired structure for developer familiarity
- **Added**: Type-safe access to different configuration categories
- **Added**: Memory-cached configuration for fast access
- **Added**: Comprehensive documentation for all settings
- **Improved**: Configuration management and accessibility
- **Enhanced**: Islamic content configuration capabilities

## Version 0.0.17 (2025-07-30)

## Version 0.0.16 (2025-07-30)
- **Added**: Prayer Times Integration System with astronomical algorithms
- **Added**: PrayerTime Model with 7 calculation methods
- **Added**: PrayerTimeController with web and API endpoints
- **Added**: Advanced prayer calculations for worldwide accuracy
- **Added**: Multiple calculation methods (MWL, ISNA, EGYPT, MAKKAH, KARACHI, TEHRAN, JAFARI)
- **Added**: User location management with preferences
- **Added**: Prayer time widgets for external websites
- **Added**: Qibla direction calculation
- **Added**: Next prayer detection
- **Added**: Multi-language support for prayer names
- **Added**: Time format options (12-hour and 24-hour)
- **Added**: High latitude adjustment for polar regions
- **Added**: Real-time statistics and performance metrics
- **Added**: Intelligent caching for prayer time calculations
- **Improved**: Prayer time accuracy and performance
- **Enhanced**: User experience with comprehensive prayer features

